        "The formula for cross-entropy loss is:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$ J=-\\sum\\limits_{k=1}^{V}y_k\\log{\\hat{y}_k} \\tag{6}$$\n",
        "\n",
        "**Implement the cross-entropy loss function.**\n",
